<H3> <TI>   24 Deputies Propose Expelling Israeli Ambassador </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC1003153494 Cairo AL-JUMHURIYAH in Arabic 6 Mar 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> NC1003153494 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo AL-JUMHURIYAH </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The People's Assembly yesterday decided to refer to 
the Arab Affairs, Foreign Relations, and National Security 
Committee a proposal by 24 members demanding that the Israeli 
ambassador in Egypt be expelled, the Egyptian ambassador in 
Israel be withdrawn, and Egyptian-Israeli relations be frozen. 

</TEXT>

