<H3> <TI>   Finance Minister Meets With Hungary's Szabo </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA1103120494 Tel Aviv 'AL HAMISHMAR in Hebrew 11 Mar 94 p 4 </F>
<F P=103> TA1103120494 </F>
<F P=104>  Tel Aviv 'AL HAMISHMAR </F>


<TEXT>
