Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Report by Ya'ir Meydan] </F>
  [Text] Finance Minister Avraham Shohat met with his 
Hungarian counterpart, Ivan Szabo, yesterday. The two men 
discussed strengthening commercial ties between the two 
countries; the activities of Israeli companies in Hungary; 
Israel's participation in Expo 96, which will take place in 
