Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Interview with Israeli Arab Knesset Member 'Abd-al-Wahhab </F>
Darawshah, by Sana' al-Imam in Damascus on 10 Mar--recorded] 
  [Excerpts] [passage omitted] [Al-Imam] As Israeli Arabs, 
how do you view the Gaza-Jericho agreement? 
  [Darawshah] First of all I object to such description. We 
are not Israeli Arabs. We are Palestinians and are citizens of 
the State of Israel. We are part of the Arab nation. 
Therefore, I hope Arab reporters and media would not use such 
