<H3> <TI>   King Husayn To Visit Qatar 20 Mar </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  JN1003082694 Amman AL-DUSTUR in Arabic 10 Mar 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> JN1003082694 </F>
<F P=104>  Amman AL-DUSTUR </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Amman--QNA--An informed source in Amman has 
confirmed that that His Majesty King Husayn will visit fraternal 
Qatar on 20 March. 
  The source told a Qatari news agency correspondent that his 
majesty will discuss with His Highness Shaykh Khalifah Bin-Hamad 
Al Thani, amir of Qatar, ways of bolstering fraternal ties 
within the single Arab family and promoting Arab solidarity. 
They will also discuss Arab, regional, and international issues. 
  This visit signifies the continuing development of fraternal 
ties between the two countries. 

