Language: <F P=105> Dari </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpt] Last night and today, the Golboddin-Dostum 
militia martyred a number of our innocent compatriots by firing 
lethal rockets into the residential areas of Kabul. A BAKHTAR 
military correspondent reports that as a result of this rocket 
attack by the militia, a number of our compatriots were also 
injured and were taken to hospitals for treatment. 
  Similarly, as a result of rocket attacks and the firing of 
mortar shells into residential areas, which continued during 
today, much damage has been inflicted on public utility 
institutions, on residents, and public property. 
