<H3> <TI>   Intelligence Post Reportedly Attacked; 7 Killed </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC1103151194 (Clandestine) Voice of Iraqi Islamic Revolution 
in Arabic 1430 GMT 11 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC1103151194 </F>
<F P=104>  (Clandestine) Voice of Iraqi Islamic Revolution 
