  [Excerpt] Cairo, 12 Mar (MENA)--The Egyptian national unity 
committee denounced last night's criminal attack on the Dayr 
al-Muharraq in al-Qusiyah, one of Egypt's sacred religious 
places respected by all Egyptians, both Muslims and Christians. 
