  The statement appealed to Muslim and Christian forces and 
bodies to rise to responsibility, condemn this criminal act and 
its perpetrators, confront this trend, and work assiduously for 
the unity of all Egyptians under the slogan of: Religion belongs 
to God and the homeland belongs to everyone. [passage omitted] 

