<H3> <TI>   'Urayqat Assails U.S. Intention To Veto Resolution </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  JN1203191194 Paris Radio Monte Carlo in Arabic 1700 GMT 12 
Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN1203191194 </F>
<F P=104>  Paris Radio Monte Carlo </F>


<TEXT>
