  [Excerpt] Dr. Sa'ib 'Urayqat, head of the Palestinian 
delegation to the Washington talks, has said that the U.S. 
hinting that it will veto the UN Security Council resolution on 
the al-Ibrahimi Mosque if the PLO does not resume the talks with 
