<F P=100> Palestinian Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   PFLP-GC Denies 2 Killed, 2 Captured in Lebanon </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  JN1203210794 (Clandestine) Al-Quds Palestinian Arab Radio in 
Arabic 1730 GMT 12 Mar 94 </F>

