<H3> <TI>   IDF Will Not Change Firing Rules on Settlers </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA1103204594 Jerusalem New Channel 2 Television Network in 
Hebrew 1800 GMT 11 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA1103204594 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem New Channel 2 Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Hebrew </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The IDF [Israel Defense Forces] will not revise the 
rules governing shooting at Jewish settlers. A senior defense 
source has told our military correspondent Roni Daniyel that the 
orders banning gunfire on Jews does not apply to cases such as 
the Hebron massacre, contrary to the testimony of the Hebron 
Border Police company commander at the Shamgar Commission 
