<F P=100> Palestinian Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   Hamas Issues `Veiled Warning' on Revenge </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA1103165494 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English 1600 GMT 11 
Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA1103165494 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Islamic militants have issued a veiled warning 
today that revenge for the Hebron massacre might come in 
Brooklyn, New York. Hamas [Islamic Resistance Movement] said in 
a leaflet distributed in the Gaza Strip that the gunman who 
attacked a van of orthodox Jews in New York last week was 
inspired by Islamic teachings. One person was killed and three 
others wounded in that attack by a 28-year old Lebanese-born 
taxi driver. 

</TEXT>

