<H3> <TI>   One `Terrorist' Killed; One Wounded in Gaza Strip </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA1503113694 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1100 GMT 15 
Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA1503113694 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Hebrew </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] One terrorist was shot dead and another seriously 
wounded in Bayt Lahiyah in the Gaza Strip during a firefight 
between terrorists and the security forces. Our correspondent 
Nisim Qeynan reports that shots were fired at a security forces 
vehicle in the Bayt Lahiyah area a short time ago. The soldiers 
returned the fire, killing the terrorist and seriously wounded 
his comrade. 
  Our correspondent adds that the security forces captured two 
Hamas [Islamic Resistance Movement] fugitives last night during 
an initiated operation in Gaza's Rimal and al-Shaykh Radwan 
neighborhoods. 

