<H3> <TI>   Iranian Forces Reportedly Fire on Shawrah Plain </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC1403162194 (Clandestine) Voice of the People of Kurdistan 
in Arabic 1530 GMT 14 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC1403162194 </F>
<F P=104>  (Clandestine) Voice of the People of Kurdistan 
