<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105>Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Shawrah Plain area in the al-Sulaymaniyah 
Governorate came under rocket fire on 11 March from Iranian 
positions. The Iranian forces fired 26 rockets at the aforesaid 
